title: PHOTO GALLERY: Daniel Murphy's 7 postseason home runs
text: > Top News PHOTO GALLERY: Daniel Murphy's 7 postseason home runs FILE - On top, in an Oct. 17, 2015, file photo, New York Mets' Daniel Murphy hits his fourth 2015 postseason home run, during the first inning of Game 1 of the National League baseball championship series against the Chicago Cubs in New York. On bottom, also in an Oct. 17, 2015, file photo, Mets' Daniel Murphy (28) is congratulated by teammate Travis d'Arnaud after hitting the home run during the first inning of Game 1 of the National League baseball championship series against the Cubs in New York. (AP Photo/File)
